  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is examining impact of pain on daily life, the ability to function and treatments&#xD;
      used for patients with interstitial cystitis/painful bladder syndrome before and after a&#xD;
      program of mindfulness and yoga, in comparison to patients who are undergoing treatment with&#xD;
      their providers.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
